description: Dave and Tommy are smoking numbers on today's show... Literally! They also share their thoughts on the new issue of Cigar Aficionado magazine, and give us the REAL 411 on all the latest cigar ratings. It's another exciting week of eating, drinking and smoking on the Cigar Authority!
